---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof vs Podium — Testimonials without the $400/mo price tag | SocialProof" description="Podium costs $399–599/mo and bundles review management with messaging. SocialProof is $9/mo and puts testimonials on your site in 5 minutes. Compare honestly." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/vs/podium">
<style>

    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #fff; color: #111; }
    nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    nav a.logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #111; text-decoration: none; }
    nav .nav-links a { margin-left: 1.5rem; color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    nav .cta-nav { background: #111; color: #fff !important; padding: .45rem 1rem; border-radius: 6px; }
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .vs-badge { display: inline-block; background: #f0f0f0; color: #555; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: .35rem .75rem; border-radius: 99px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .hero h1 span { color: #4f46e5; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; color: #444; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
    .hero-cta { display: inline-block; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    .hero-cta:hover { background: #3730a3; }
    .price-callout { display: inline-flex; gap: 2rem; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .price-callout .item { text-align: center; }
    .price-callout .item .price { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; }
    .price-callout .item .label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #777; margin-top: .2rem; }
    .price-callout .item.socialproof .price { color: #4f46e5; }
    .price-callout .item.other .price { color: #dc2626; }
    section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .compare-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .compare-table th { padding: .75rem 1rem; text-align: left; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; color: #888; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; }
    .compare-table th:nth-child(2) { color: #4f46e5; }
    .compare-table td { padding: .85rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; font-size: 0.97rem; vertical-align: top; }
    .compare-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .compare-table td:first-child { color: #555; font-weight: 500; }
    .yes { color: #16a34a; font-weight: 600; }
    .no { color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; }
    .partial { color: #d97706; font-weight: 600; }
    .winner-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .winner-card { border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.75rem; }
    .winner-card.socialproof { background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #86efac; }
    .winner-card.other { background: #fafafa; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; }
    .winner-card h3 { margin: 0 0 .5rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .winner-card p { margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #444; line-height: 1.5; }
    .verdict { background: #f0fdf4; border: 2px solid #86efac; border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .verdict h3 { margin: 0 0 .75rem; color: #15803d; font-size: 1.2rem; }
    .verdict p { margin: 0; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.65; color: #333; }
    .faq { border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0; padding-top: 2rem; }
    .faq-item { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .faq-item h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 .5rem; }
    .faq-item p { margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #444; line-height: 1.65; }
    .cta-section { text-align: center; background: #f5f3ff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 3rem 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
    .cta-section p { font-size: 1.05rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .cta-btn { display: inline-block; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: 1rem 2.5rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .persona-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .persona-card { border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; }
    .persona-card h3 { margin: 0 0 .5rem; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .persona-card p { margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.55; }
    footer { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; color: #999; font-size: 0.85rem; border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0; margin-top: 4rem; }
    footer a { color: #777; text-decoration: none; }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .winner-grid, .persona-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .price-callout { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
    }
  
</style>
<div class="hero">
  <span class="vs-badge">SocialProof vs Podium</span>
  <h1>Podium costs <span>$399/mo.</span><br>We cost $9.</h1>
  <p>Podium is a powerful messaging and review platform built for multi-location businesses. If you just need testimonials on your website, it's 40× more than you need.</p>

  <div class="price-callout">
    <div class="item socialproof">
      <div class="price">$9/mo</div>
      <div class="label">SocialProof Pro</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item other">
      <div class="price">$399/mo</div>
      <div class="label">Podium Essentials</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register" class="hero-cta">Try SocialProof free →</a>
</div>

<section>
  <h2>What is Podium?</h2>
  <p>Podium is a customer communication platform built for local and multi-location businesses — think dental chains, auto dealerships, plumbers with 20 trucks. It bundles SMS marketing, review requests, web chat, team messaging, and payment collection into one dashboard.</p>
  <p>That's genuinely powerful if you're running a 10-location franchise that needs one inbox for every location's text conversations. But for a single-location business or a freelancer who just wants customers' words on their website — it's a very expensive, very complex hammer for a small nail.</p>

  <h2>Head-to-head comparison</h2>
  <table class="compare-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Feature</th>
        <th>SocialProof</th>
        <th>Podium</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Starting price</td>
        <td class="yes">Free (1 widget)</td>
        <td class="no">$399/mo (annual contract)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Setup time</td>
        <td class="yes">5 minutes</td>
        <td class="no">Days — onboarding call, integrations, team setup</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Embed testimonials on your site</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Core feature — one &lt;script&gt; tag</td>
        <td class="partial">⚠ Review widgets available, but that's a side feature</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Collect text testimonials</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Via shareable link</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Via SMS request</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>SMS marketing</td>
        <td class="no">Not included</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Core feature</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Team inbox / messaging</td>
        <td class="no">Not included</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Core feature</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Payment collection</td>
        <td class="no">Not included</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Via Podium Payments</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Multiple locations</td>
        <td class="no">Single business focus</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Built for multi-location</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Google review syndication</td>
        <td class="no">Not included</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Pushes reviews to Google</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Contract required</td>
        <td class="yes">No — month-to-month</td>
        <td class="no">Yes — annual contract</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Shopify / WordPress embed</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Works on any site</td>
        <td class="partial">⚠ Limited widget options</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>No-code setup</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Paste one script tag</td>
        <td class="partial">⚠ Requires onboarding help</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Who wins for what</h2>
  <div class="winner-grid">
    <div class="winner-card socialproof">
      <h3>🟢 SocialProof wins for</h3>
      <p>Solo freelancers, coaches, small agencies, local service businesses, Shopify stores, and anyone who just needs a beautiful testimonial widget on their site without a monthly sales call or annual contract.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="winner-card other">
      <h3>⚪ Podium wins for</h3>
      <p>Multi-location franchises, dental or medical groups, auto dealerships — businesses that need unified SMS + reviews + team messaging + payments across many locations, and have the budget for an enterprise platform.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="verdict">
    <h3>The honest verdict</h3>
    <p>Podium isn't a bad product — it's a category leader for what it does. But "what it does" is run a multi-channel communications operation for a local service business with significant revenue and headcount. If that's you, get Podium.</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">If you're a photographer, a coach, a freelance designer, a small agency, or a Shopify store owner who wants real customer quotes on their site — you'll pay $399/mo for maybe 10% of what Podium offers. SocialProof gives you that 10% for $9/mo.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>The pricing reality</h2>
  <p>Podium's Essentials plan starts at $399/mo, billed annually — that's <strong>$4,788/year</strong>. Their Core and Pro plans are $599+ and $799+/mo. There is no monthly billing option on the entry plan, which means you're committing before you've seen results.</p>
  <p>SocialProof is $9/mo with no annual commitment and a free tier that includes one permanent widget. You can be live with testimonials today, for free, in the time it takes to read this page.</p>

  <h2>Who uses each product</h2>
  <div class="persona-grid">
    <div class="persona-card">
      <h3>SocialProof is built for</h3>
      <p>A freelance copywriter putting client logos and testimonials on their portfolio. A yoga instructor embedding a testimonials wall on their Squarespace. A plumber running a 3-person crew who wants Google reviews to appear on their site. A Shopify store owner who needs a "customers love us" section above the fold.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="persona-card">
      <h3>Podium is built for</h3>
      <p>A 12-location dental group coordinating patient communication across all locations. A large auto dealer group managing incoming text leads and routing them to the right sales rep. A franchise that needs every location to collect reviews from the same unified dashboard.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>What SocialProof actually does</h2>
  <p>You get a shareable link. You send it to customers. They leave a testimonial — their name, their words, a photo if they want. You go to your dashboard, approve it, and it appears automatically in your widget. No app for your customers to install. No login required from them. Works in 5 minutes.</p>
  <p>Then you paste one script tag into your website, Shopify store, Squarespace site, WordPress page, or anywhere that accepts HTML. Your testimonials appear, styled to match your site, and update automatically as you collect more.</p>

  <div class="faq">
    <h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Does SocialProof replace Podium for local service businesses?</h3>
      <p>It depends what you use Podium for. If you're using Podium mainly for review requests and displaying testimonials on your site, SocialProof is a direct and cheaper alternative. If you rely heavily on Podium's SMS inbox, team chat, and payment features, those aren't part of SocialProof — we're purely focused on collecting and displaying testimonials on your website.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Can SocialProof send review requests via SMS like Podium?</h3>
      <p>SocialProof uses shareable links — you paste or text the link to customers, and they fill in their testimonial via a web form. We don't send automated SMS blasts on your behalf, which keeps things simple and avoids TCPA compliance headaches. For most small businesses, a link sent via text is easier to set up than a Podium SMS campaign.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Does Podium let me embed testimonials on my own website?</h3>
      <p>Podium has review widgets, but it's not their focus — their product is built around the inbox and review request flow. SocialProof's entire purpose is getting your customers' words onto your website in the best-looking, easiest-to-manage way possible.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Can I try SocialProof before committing?</h3>
      <p>Yes. The free tier includes one permanent widget with unlimited testimonials on it. No credit card required. You'll have working testimonials on your site before you decide if the $9/mo Pro upgrade makes sense for you.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>What if I'm currently paying for Podium and not using half the features?</h3>
      <p>That's the most common reason people find us. If your Podium usage is basically "send review request, collect testimonial, paste it somewhere" — you're paying $399/mo for a $9/mo use case. Switch, save $4,700/year, and get a product where testimonials are the whole point, not an afterthought.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="cta-section">
    <h2>Testimonials on your site. Today. Free.</h2>
    <p>No contracts. No onboarding calls. No enterprise sales process.<br>Start free, be live in 5 minutes.</p>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register" class="cta-btn">Get started free →</a>
    <p style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.875rem; color: #777;">Free forever for 1 active widget · No credit card required</p>
  </div>

  <p style="text-align: center; color: #999; font-size: 0.85rem;">Pricing information sourced from Podium's public website. Verify current pricing at podium.com. SocialProof is not affiliated with Podium.</p>
</section>
</Base>
